<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN239-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. nampineṭuñceḻinaṉaip pēreyiṉmuṟuvalār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN239">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>toṭiyuṭaiya tōṇmaṇantaṉaṉ</l>
<l>kaṭikāviṟ pūccūṭiṉaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṇkamaḻuñ cāntunīviṉaṉ</l>
<l>ceṟṟōrai vaḻitaputtaṉa</l>
<l>ṉaṭṭōrai yuyarpukūṟiṉaṉ</l>
<l>valiyareṉa vaḻimoḻiyalaṉ</l>
<l>meliyareṉa mīkkūṟalaṉ</l>
<l>piṟaraittā ṉirappaṟiyala</l>
<l>ṉirantōrkku maṟuppaṟiyalaṉ</l>
<l>vēntuṭai yavaiyat tōṅkupukaḻ tōṟṟiṉaṉ</l>
<l>varupaṭai yetirtāṅkiṉaṉ</l>
<l>peyarpaṭai puṟaṅkaṇṭaṉaṉ</l>
<l>kaṭumpariya mākkaṭaviṉa</l>
<l>ṉeṭunteruviṟ tērvaḻaṅkiṉa</l>
<l>ṉōṅkiyala kaḷiṟūrntaṉaṉ</l>
<l>ṟīñceṟi tacumputolaicciṉaṉ</l>
<l>pāṇuvappap pacitīrttaṉaṉ</l>
<l>mayakkuṭaiya moḻiviṭuttaṉaṉ</l>
<l>ceypa vellāñ ceytaṉa ṉākali</l>
<l>ṉiṭuka voṉṟō cuṭuka voṉṟō</l>
<l>paṭuvaḻip paṭukavip pukaḻveyyōṉ ṟalaiyē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>He united with [those whose] shoulders possess armlets. (1)</l>
<l>He wore flowers from the fragrant groves. (2)</l>
<l>He smeared [his chest] with cool fragrant sandal. (3)</l>
<l>He destroyed the path of the dead. (4)</l>
<l>He spoke high about his friends. (5)</l>
<l>He praised [them] as strong. (6)</l>
<l>He lauded [them] as gentle. (7)</l>
<l>He did not know of begging from others. (8)</l>
<l>He did not know of refusing beggars. (9)</l>
<l>He made high glory appear in the king’s assembly. (10)</l>
<l>He endured armies coming against [him]. (11)</l>
<l>He saw the back of armies turning back. (12)</l>
<l>He drove fast-gaited horses. (13)</l>
<l>He moved on a chariot through long streets. (14)</l>
<l>He mounted tall-natured elephants. (15) </l>
<l>He demolished sweet tight? pots [of toddy]. (16)</l>
<l>When rejoicing in melodies he ended hunger. (17)</l>
<l>He dismissed confusing words. (18)</l>
<l>Because he did all that could be done, (19)</l>
<l>Let them put [him] down or let them burn [it]. (20)</l>
<l>Let it go the way it goes, the head of this man keen on fame. (21)</l>
</lg>
    </div>
